[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"Judge of the man by this one trait.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "Well, he returned to Florida, and, truth to tell, was used by mr Willis with consideration and kindness, eating at his table, sleeping under his roof.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "At the end of some months a terrible typhus fever broke out in the plantation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "Out of thirty negroes dangerously affected by this fatal disease, only two perished.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "What shall I tell you more?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "Afterwards a deep and mutual love repaid him the debt of gratitude.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "David's taste was too refined to allow him to boast of his happiness before the time when he should marry Cecily, which was to be when she had turned her sixteenth year.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000001_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000001_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "The black comforted her, and instantly went to mr Willis to request her hand in marriage.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"He did.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "David talked of his love,--love so long and tenderly shared, and the planter shrugged his shoulders; David urged, but it was all in vain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "He entreated,--supplicated, and his master lost his temper.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000003_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000003_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "David, blushing to humiliate himself further, spake in a firm tone of his services and disinterestedness,--that he had been contented with a very slender salary.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000003_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000003_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "mr Willis was desperately enraged, and, telling him he was a contumacious slave, threatened him with the chain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"Really, this attack seems providential.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "The desperate condition of the man was quite deserved by him.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"The malady made fearful strides.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"Horrible, but by no means astonishing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"Such conduct was dictated alike by revenge and jealousy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"Well, what followed?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"In my life I never saw so distressing a spectacle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000017_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000017_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "The colonist said to him, with cruel irony, 'Well, doctor, how goes it?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000017_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000017_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "'God?' replied the planter, bursting into a loud fit of laughter, 'tell him, then,--tell God to come and snatch you from my power!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000017_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000017_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "I defy him!' Then Willis, overcome by fury and intoxication, shook his fist to heaven, and said, in blasphemous language, 'Yes, I defy God to carry off my slaves before they are dead!'\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"The man was mad as well as brutal.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"We were utterly disgusted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "This dungeon was situated, as well as the house, on the seashore.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000019_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000019_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "Strange contrast!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000019_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000019_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "These men torture their slaves, and yet do not take any precaution against them, but sleep with doors and windows open.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000019_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000019_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "We easily got access to the sleeping room of the planter, which was lighted on the inside by a small glass lamp.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000019_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000019_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "'You have to night defied God to carry off your two victims before their death, and he has taken them,' said monseigneur.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000019_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000019_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "God will judge between us.' We then retreated, leaving mr Willis stupefied, motionless, and believing himself under the influence of a dream.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"All this is as assailable and as justifiable as the punishment of the Schoolmaster, my worthy squire.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "And had not this adventure any consequences?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"It could not.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"They say he tried to kill his wife.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "So now, my dear Murphy, farewell till the evening.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "Will they have soon completed their respective missions?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7239/63500/7239_63500_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7239",
        "content": "\"You know that monseigneur will keep them away as long as possible, that he may enjoy more solitude and liberty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7239_63500_000035_000002",
